     1	# Plan: Lecture 10 — Cluster Analysis with Interactive Widgets
     2	
     3	## TL;DR
     4	Create a Quarto revealjs lecture on cluster analysis with embedded OJS widgets for step-by-step visualization of hierarchical, K-means, K-medoids, and DBSCAN clustering. Three data sources: synthetic 2D data (generated live), D&D Monsters from TidyTuesday (lecture demo), and Qatar Cars from TidyTuesday (student exercise). Parquet export for modern workflows. Includes 2026 best practices: HDBSCAN, tidyclust, UMAP, bootstrap cluster stability.
