     8	## Architecture
     9	
    10	**Format**: Quarto revealjs (.qmd) — supports native `{ojs}` code blocks for Observable JS widgets alongside `{r}` chunks.
    11	
    12	**File structure**:
    13	```
    14	lectures/
    15	  lecture10.qmd                    # Main lecture slides
    16	  lecture10_widgets/
    17	    hierarchical-widget.js         # OJS: step-by-step agglomerative clustering
    18	    kmeans-kmedoids-widget.js      # OJS: step-by-step K-means / K-medoids
    19	    dbscan-widget.js               # OJS: step-by-step DBSCAN with epsilon viz
    20	    cluster-comparison-widget.js   # OJS: choose method, see clustering result
    21	    bootstrap-stability-widget.js  # OJS: hierarchical bootstrap stability
    22	```
