   171	## Decisions
   172	
   173	- **Format**: Quarto revealjs — user chose OJS integration
   174	- **Lecture dataset**: D&D Monsters (TidyTuesday 2025-05-27) — 6 ability scores + HP/CR/speed, `type` as ground truth, engaging, needs scaling
   175	- **Student dataset**: Qatar Cars (TidyTuesday 2025-12-09) — 10 numeric features, `type`/`enginetype` as ground truth, practical, modern SI units
   176	- **Data loading**: Direct `read_csv()` from raw GitHub URLs in the .qmd — no local storage needed except parquet demo
   177	- **DBSCAN**: Full theory + R code + widget per user request
   178	- **Scope includes**: Dissimilarity, hierarchical, K-means, K-medoids, silhouettes, DBSCAN, HDBSCAN, UMAP, bootstrap stability, 5 OJS widgets
   179	- **Scope excludes**: Association rules (lecture 11), GMMs, spectral clustering
