   181	## 2026 Best Practices
   182	
   183	1. **tidyclust** — tidymodels-native clustering (`k_means()`, `hier_clust()` with fit/augment)
   184	2. **HDBSCAN** — auto-ε density clustering via `dbscan::hdbscan()`
   185	3. **UMAP** — `uwot::umap()` for visualizing high-dim clusters
   186	4. **Parquet** — `arrow` package for modern columnar data
   187	5. **Bootstrap cluster stability** — adjusted Rand index across resamples
   188	6. **Quarto + OJS** — modern reproducible presentations with interactive JS
